extension.description.full.message:
PreMiD is a simple, configurable utility that allows you to show what you're doing on the web in your Discord now playing status.

For example, when you start watching a video on YouTube, our extension grabs all the information needed from the page and sends it to our application, which then sets the status on your Discord profile.

PreMiD supports more than 500 websites and is still going thanks to its strong community that adds new Presences every day.

To use PreMiD, you need to add this extension and install the official PreMiD application found on our website. This is due to constraints in the way Discord’s Rich Presence SDK works.

